Description
-----------

Forces this surfaces with this material keyword to cast shadows.

Usage
-----

In the global section of your material shader type...

    forceShadows

Parameters
----------

Not Available.

Notes
-----

This keyword is useful for forcing materials to cast shadows that would otherwise not. For instance, textures/common/nodraw does not cast shadows but could be made to through use of this global keyword.

